name: Jedi Survivor
Text: 'When deployed, you may not initiate battle here this turn. While at opponent''s site, adds one [Light Side Force] and one [Dark Side Force]. May ''swing'' lightsabers for free. May never be won in sabacc. Immune to attrition < 5. End of turn: Use 1 to maintain OR Lose 1 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.',
